{"tid":965922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為用iPhone發Tweet賀新年","createTime":"2019-01-02T11:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T13:33:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"feac80a4998920edb7dd726a499c7806b2338c02","tid":965922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190102/20581886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190102%2F20581886&d=a%2ByH%2B75UN8%2B%2FnnxGwmERpIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8317b43c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190102%2F20581886&h=29f02847\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190102/20581886</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月02日 <br />\n<br />\n華為用iPhone發Tweet賀新年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190102/large/02ck30p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190102%2Flarge%2F02ck30p.jpg&h=687387f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年備受孟晚舟事件困擾的內地電訊巨商華為，在年末最後一天竟用蘋果iPhone於Twitter發新年祝福。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民嘲員工倒米<br />\n<br />\n華為察覺後，迅速刪除貼文，但已被美網絡紅人Marques Brownlee截圖瘋傳（圖）。事件讓支持華為的國人難堪，難怪有內地網民忍不住嘲諷，原來華為中人多是「心繫」蘋果的！<br />\n<br />\n華為12月31日11時31分於Twitter發佈該貼文，以全體員工名義送上新年祝福。但該貼文下方卻留下「自Twitter的iPhone客戶端發出」（Via Twitter for iPhone）的標記。雖然華為很快刪除該貼文，但它還是被網絡紅人Marques Brownlee截圖流傳，隨即引起熱議。有網友認為，華為在官方社交媒體使用競爭對手的產品，如同倒「自己米」，說穿了連員工也不用公司產品。不過，也有網友指，三星（Samsung）和蘋果（Apple）亦曾多次犯過類似錯誤，蘋果公司最近還用Android設備在Twitter發文，推廣自家產品Apple Music。<br />\n<br />\n很多內地網友都形容，今次事件是華為的公關災難：「你這是打了母親的臉！必須嚴懲！」「誇華為是工作，用蘋果是生活。」根據去年8月1日國際市場調查機構IDC報告，華為同年上季智能手機出貨量大增逾四成，市場佔有達16%，首次超越蘋果，僅次於三星的21%。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/微博  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n鐵路訂票官網洩470萬用戶資料"},{"pid":"f2dc44451f5605fa7cfea8bec9a62f5763947663","tid":965922,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"iPhone is 華為 owned"},{"pid":"59985ff6db399670dcb7ac976907a8709d1ab796","tid":965922,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"華為又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yHj4r0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yHj4r0.jpg&h=e092f2a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"744bb185cafe8e79e2a57c0bb90f19a92c04ef6b","tid":965922,"uid":142067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59985ff6db399670dcb7ac976907a8709d1ab796","tid":965922,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"華為又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yHj4r0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yHj4r0.jpg&h=e092f2a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}